metadata.editComments: I would put it in E minor but in acapella it mostly hits the note G, and as subdominant and dominant chords it has C and D instead of Am and Bm, which doesn't make this a "very sad" song; so this one would work as G Major. Because if you transform it from E minor to E major it sounds very C# minor. A case similar to Ocean Eyes by Billie Eilish.
